{"build_type":"library","description":"Load one native object by symbol name into the loader's link region and record it in the closure, then transitively load its dependency closure. Idempotent (returns immediately if the name is already in g_ld_map, allocating nothing). For a genuinely new root it allocates a thread-local worklist buffer from its own arena (buf[0]=top, buf[1]=cap, buf[2..]=pending names), seeds it with the name, and drives an explicit iterative closure walk (import-dependency-closure-worklist-iteration) instead of native mutual recursion, so the loader stack stays O(1) regardless of dependency-chain depth. A missing file is a fatal unresolved-dependency error. Each loaded object's code is copied into g_ld_region at g_ld_cursor (16-byte aligned), map[name]=base recorded, the object stamped with __base and appended to g_ld_loaded for the later patch pass.","module_name":"import-named-object-inside-closure-environment","package_name":"import-named-object-inside-closure-environment","function_definitions":{"import-named-object-inside-closure-environment":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"name","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"zero","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"one","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":1},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"two","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":2},{"instruction_type":"global_read","dest":"map","name":"g_ld_map"},{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"locate-named-member-inside-mapping","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"map"},{"kind":"var","value":"name"}],"result_assignment_variable":"existing","result_type":"i64"},{"instruction_type":"conditional_branch","condition_type":"numeric_compare","operator":"!=","lhs":{"value":"existing"},"rhs":{"value":"zero"},"branch_on_success":[{"instruction_type":"return_statement","return_payload":{"value":"zero"}}],"branch_on_failure":[]},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"cap","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":262142},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"bufsize","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":2097152},{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"allocate-character-buffer-inside-memory-arena","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"bufsize"}],"result_assignment_variable":"buf","result_type":"i64"},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"k_of","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string","source_target":"worklist_overflow"},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"k_dom","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string","source_target":"import-closure"},{"instruction_type":"conditional_branch","condition_type":"numeric_compare","operator":"==","lhs":{"value":"buf"},"rhs":{"value":"zero"},"branch_on_success":[{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"report_error_and_exit","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"k_of"},{"kind":"var","value":"k_dom"}]}],"branch_on_failure":[]},{"instruction_type":"array_write","base":"buf","index":"one","value":"cap","scale":8},{"instruction_type":"array_write","base":"buf","index":"two","value":"name","scale":8},{"instruction_type":"array_write","base":"buf","index":"zero","value":"one","scale":8},{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"import-dependency-closure-worklist-iteration","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"buf"}],"result_assignment_variable":"_r","result_type":"i64"},{"instruction_type":"return_statement","return_payload":{"value":"zero"}}]}}}